unit: manifest entry
id: has_hdmi_rx_v4l2
_name: HDMI RX (Input) via mainline V4L2
_prompt: Does this machine expose HDMI RX through a mainline V4L2 node?
value-type: bool

unit: manifest entry
id: has_hdmi_rx_specific
_name: HDMI RX (Input) via a platform-specific backend
_prompt: Does this machine use a platform-specific HDMI RX backend (needs the HDMIRX_BACKEND variable, e.g. genio)?
value-type: bool
